\c 28
\s Isaka anotuma Jakove kuHarani
\p
\v 1 Zvino Isaka wakadana Jakove, ndokumuropafadza, ndokumuraira ndokuti kwaari: Usawana mukadzi pavakunda veKenani\x + 24.3.\x*.
\v 2 Simuka\x + Hos. 12.12.\x*, enda kuPadhani-Aramu\x + 25.20; 48.7.\x*, kuimba yaBhetueri\x + 22.23.\x* baba vamai vako, uye uzvitorere kubva ikoko mukadzi kubva kuvakunda vaRabhani, hanzvadzi yamai vako\x + 24.29.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino Mwari Wemasimbaose ngaakuropafadze, agokuberekesa, nekukuwanza, kuti uve ungano yemarudzi\x + 17.1.\x*;
\v 4 agokupa ropafadzo yaAbhurahama\x + 12.2.\x*, kwauri nekuchizvarwa chako pamwe newe\x + 28.1,3.\x*; kuti ugare nhaka yenyika yeutorwa hwako, Mwari yaakapa kuna Abhurahama.
\v 5 Isaka ndokuendesa Jakove, iye ndokuenda kuPadhani-Aramu kuna Rabhani mwanakomana waBhetueri muSiriya, hanzvadzi yaRabheka, mai vaJakove naEsau.
\p
\v 6 Zvino Esau wakaona kuti Isaka waropafadza Jakove\x + 28.1,3.\x*, ndokumuendesa kuPadhani-Aramu kunozvitorera kubva ikoko mukadzi, paakamuropafadza wakamuraira achiti: Usatora mukadzi kuvakunda veKenani;
\v 7 uye kuti Jakove wakateerera baba vake namai vake, ndokuenda kuPadhani-Aramu.
\v 8 Esau ndokuona kuti vakunda veKenani vaiva vakaipa pameso aIsaka baba vake\x + 24.3; 26.35.\x*.
\v 9 Naizvozvo Esau wakaenda kuna Ishimaeri, ndokuzvitorera Maharati\x + 36.3; 26.34.\x* mukunda waIshimaeri, mwanakomana waAbhurahama, hanzvadzi yaNebhayoti\x + 25.13; 36.3.\x* ave mukadzi \add wake\add* pamusoro pevakadzi vake.
\p
\v 10 Zvino Jakove wakabuda kubva paBheeri-Shebha\x + 26.23,33.\x*, ndokuenda kuHarani\x + Mab. 7.2.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino wakasvika panzvimbo, ndokurarapo, nokuti zuva raiva ravira. Ndokutora \add ibwe\add* pamabwe enzvimbo iyo, ndokuita mutsago wake, ndokurara panzvimbo iyo.
\v 12 Zvino wakarota\x + 37.5,9; 40.5; 41.1. Job. 33.15.\x*, uye tarira, danhiko ramiswa panyika, nemusoro waro uchibata matenga, zvino tarira, vatumwa vaMwari vachikwira nekuburuka pariri\x + Joh. 1.51.\x*.
\v 13 Zvino tarira, Jehovha wakamira pamusoro paro\x + 35.1; 48.3.\x*, ndokuti: Ndini Jehovha Mwari waAbhurahama baba vako, naMwari waIsaka\x + 26.24; 24.12.\x*; nyika yaurere pairi ndichaipa kwauri, nekuchizvarwa chako\x + 13.15.\x*;
\v 14 uye chizvarwa chako chichaita seguruva renyika\x + 13.16.\x*; zvino uchapararira kumavirazuva nekumabvazuva nekumaodzanyemba nekuchamhembe\x + 13.14. Det. 12.20.\x*; uye mauri nemuchizvarwa chako mhuri dzose dzepanyika dzicharopafadzwa\x + 12.3; 18.18; 22.18; 26.4.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino tarira, ndinewe\x + 26.24; 31.3; 28.20.\x*, uye ndichakuchengeta kwese kwaunoenda, nekukudzosera kunyika ino\x + 35.6.\x*; nokuti handingakusii\x + Det. 31.6,8. Josh. 1.5. 1 Madz. 8.57. 1 Makor. 28.20. VaHeb. 13.5.\x* kusvika ndaita izvo zvandataura kwauri.
\v 16 Zvino Jakove wakapepuka pahope dzake, ndokuti: Zvirokwazvo Jehovha ari panzvimbo ino\x + Eki. 3.5. Josh. 5.15.\x*, asi ini ndanga ndisingazivi.
\v 17 Zvino wakatya, ndokuti: Nzvimbo ino inotyisa zvakadini! Haisi chimwe chinhu kunze kweimba yaMwari, uye iri isuwo rematenga.
\v 18 Jakove ndokumuka mangwanani-ngwanani, ndokutora ibwe raaiva aita mutsago wake, ndokurimisa kuva mbiru\x + 31.13,45; 35.14. 2 Zvak. 18.18.\x*, ndokudira mafuta pamusoro penhongonya yaro\x + Rev. 8.10,11. Num. 7.1.\x*.
\v 19 Zvino wakatumidza zita renzvimbo iyo Bheteri\x + Vato. 1.23,26.\x*; asi zita reguta pakutanga raiva Ruzi.
\v 20 Jakove ndokupika mhiko\x + 31.13. 2 Zvak. 15.8.\x* achiti: Kana Mwari akava neni, ndokundichengeta panzira iyi yandinoenda, uye akandipa chingwa chekudya, nechipfeko chekupfeka\x + 28.15.\x*;
\v 21 kuti ndidzokere nerugare kuimba yababa vangu\x + Vato. 11.31. 2 Zvak. 15.7-9; 19.30.\x*, ipapo Jehovha achava Mwari wangu\x + Det. 26.17.\x*.
\v 22 Zvino iri ibwe randamisa kuva mbiru richava imba yaMwari\x + 35.7,14.\x*; nezvose zvamuchandipa, zvirokwazvo ndichapa chegumi kwamuri\x + 14.20. Rev. 27.30.\x*.